e to Steel City</h4>\n                          <p>\nCollect UI has added a new daily inspiration to their collection. Introducing \'Sign Up\' by Leisy Vidal. Making it onto the site\'s front page, this Orlando designer captures the gritty essence of Steel City in this clean UI display.</p>\n                          <a href=\"https://us9.campaign-archive.com/?u=7aca85dad056373aad529face&amp;id=8b97b11003\" target=\"_blank\">Read More</a>\n                          <br><br>\n                          <h4>\nLet\'s Be Frank on This Barbie Site Launch</h4>\n                          <p>\nOkay, my first reaction opening this email This chick still got more style than me.</p>\n                          <p>\nIm a fan of Barbie. I\'m also a web designer. So when I received an email of Barbies latest site launch my two worlds came together and I was excited. Come with me and lets discover this new site launch. Not into either, well have you checked out my writing style? This is one storytelling you\'ll get a kick out of.</p>\n                          <a href=\"https://medium.com/@Katdelorme/lets-be-frank-on-this-barbie-site-launch-8a78f94d13f9#.4vw7azkle\" target=\"_blank\">Read More</a>\n                        </td>\n                      </tr>\n                    </tbody>\n                  </table>\n                  <!-- Footer -->\n                  <table class=\"row\">\n                    <tbody>\n                      <tr>\n                        <td>\n                          <img src=\"https://images.pexels.com/photos/340901/pexels-photo-340901.jpeg?w=940&amp;h=650&amp;dpr=2&amp;auto=compress&amp;cs=tinysrgb\" alt=\"Learn more at ASUprepdigital.asu.edu\" style=\"width: 600px !important; min-width: 600px !important; max-width: 600px !important;min-height:100px;\" width=\"600\" height=\"100\">\n                        </td>\n                      </tr>\n                    </tbody>\n                  </table>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n      